(firstQuint)Study of KW-0761 Versus Vorinostat in Relapsed/Refractory CTCL.

 Phase 3 randomized study to compare the progression free survival of subjects with relapsed/refractory CTCL who receive KW-0761 versus those who receive vorinostat.

 Subjects who progress on vorinostat will be allowed to cross over to KW-0761 upon progression.

